parameters:
...That thing from yesterday, it wasn't a dream,
right? I have to work hard from today to gather
faith...!

...First, let's have breakfast. I won't have
energy if I'm hungry. Let's go downstairs.
What would you like to do?
if(s[2])\c[27]I'm going to masturbate and go to sleep
(I wonder what we should do today...?)
I guess we'll stop after all
Which toy would you like to use?

Hehe... This person's videos are interesting Oh,
'Infiltrating a Castella Factory'! This video
looks interesting too!

What's all the fuss about? Did you find something
interesting despite your age?

Yes, recently I started watching various videos on
a video sharing site, and surprisingly, they are
quite interesting.

Hmm, this kind of service has been rapidly
expanding in recent years.

There was a time when I was obsessed with it,
spending most of my days filming videos and
posting them.

...It's scary how much it can consume your life.
If you spend less time working, there won't be
much left for hobbies...

What are you saying? Nowadays, big money is
flowing into these kinds of websites.

Even the ones before me were able to live quite
comfortably thanks to the revenue from videos.

Well, maybe I could make money by posting videos
like those people do Hehe... just kidding, that's
impossible for me...

No problem. With your appearance alone, you could
easily make money just by having casual
conversations.

R-Really?! Could it be that Rei-san is
knowledgeable about those kinds of things...?
Of course. Who do you think I am?

If I were to produce, you could become a popular
streamer who earns hundreds of thousands of yen in
revenue with each stream.

(Certainly... I remember hearing something about
how streaming sites have been growing rapidly even
on TV lately...)

(I can't guarantee that I'll always be healthy...
So, I should work hard now and save up as much as
possible...!)

How about it? Wanna earn some pocket money with
me?

Hmm... Well then, let's get started... on which
streaming site and the tips to use...

Alright, let's get excited and start the
livestream. But first, let's take the next step
here.

Yes, I believe we were able to understand a bit
about paid chat from the previous livestream.

From this time on, we will delve deeper into that.
Specifically...

(Last time, I ended up showing my breasts... If
possible, I would like to do a casual and ordinary
chat stream like other streamers...)

(Yeah, like talking about cooking or discussing
the novels I've recently read...)

(But, when it comes to naughty talk, I get a lot
of paid comments... Honestly, compared to others,
my streams have a lot of that...)

(.....No, while it's true that I initially did
this to earn some extra money, recently I've
started wanting to entertain the people who watch
me... I've started feeling that way.)

(......Well, honestly, it's not that I mind
getting a reaction when I do something naughty,
but it feels like it's not based on my actual
skills and that bothers me. So, I should focus on
having proper conversations...)

Well, I would usually give you my usual advice...
but unfortunately, I'm a busy person and won't be
able to come back until tonight.

This is a great opportunity. Think of everything
from scratch and try to liven up the broadcast.

....Yes! Since it's a special occasion, I'll try
to liven up the broadcast with just my talk,
without anything explicit.

Oh... It's true that talking about explicit things
every time can get boring. Let's have high
expectations for your storytelling skills, shall
we?
Yes, please leave it to me.

(Hehehe.... I hope there won't be any
troubles...)
Let's make today's stream a normal one...

It was going well until earlier... but then I
received something like that...

(We still have some time until the stream
starts...)

After the event ends, if you press the Q key, you
can hear Ayako's soliloquy about that event.

Basically, it doesn't affect the game progress if
you don't listen to it, but she might whisper
something that could lead to hints for capturing.

Also, be aware that if you fall asleep at home or
listen to the event-related soliloquy
once,\c[2]she won't whisper it again.\c[0] So
please be careful if you want to hear all the
conversations.

(My breasts are getting swollen... Should I
squeeze them...?)
I guess I'll stop after all
